{"id":239041,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-各地访民在北京为邓志波发起募捐活动（/","date":"2012-07-10T17:01:23Z","modified":"2012-07-10T17:01:23Z","title":"维权网 | 各地访民在北京为邓志波发起募捐活动（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lqECnOLc06U/T_xG6HKX2CI/AAAAAAAAJJk/RFD05PFLe68/s1600/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%AC%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E9%85%89%E5%8D%95%E9%97%B9%E6%90%9E%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E5%AE%A3%E4%BC%A0%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8.JPG\"></a><br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"208\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lqECnOLc06U/T_xG6HKX2CI/AAAAAAAAJJk/RFD05PFLe68/s320/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%AC%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E9%85%89%E5%8D%95%E9%97%B9%E6%90%9E%E5%8B%9F%E9%9B%86%E5%AE%A3%E4%BC%A0%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8.JPG\" width=\"320\" /> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>在京访民前往酉单闹搞募集宣传活动</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span><span>维权网信息员关小令报道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>10<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">上午</span></span><span>，在京各地访民倡导发起为身患肝癌的吉林访民邓志波募捐活动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>希望得到社会爱心人士的经济帮助</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>同时揭露当今中国腐败分子扼杀反腐人士的残酷手段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span><span>以警醒民众认清反腐维权的历史重任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加集体募捐宣传活动，是由河南访民胡醒爱、李明翠、贾拥；河北访民段淑兰；江苏访民邵允黎；吉林访民刘凤琴；天津访民郑建慧、冯淑云；湖北访民郑大靖等人共同发起，并制作宣传横幅，介绍维权反腐访民邓志波受害致病经过。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邓志波长期以来不顾打压迫害，坚持反腐败维权，积极帮助各地访民，在访民中享有一定的威望。募捐内容如下：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>募捐<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>反腐勇士邓志波，因举报吉林省营成煤矿假报破产，国有资产流失问题，被打击报复，拘留、劳教、陷害。劳教期间，把邓志波和患有黄疸型肝炎的劳教人员同关一室，致使其传染上肝炎。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现邓志波肝硬化，肝囊肿，近来病情恶化无钱医治，随时有生命危险。敬请社会各界及媒体给予关注。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7993135286473101216?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/36ba4226BBE58AA8.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}